videos.headline: Holyfield bounces left, walks in TD
videos.description: Georgia RB Elijah Holyfield cuts to the edge and trots in the 5-yard touchdown, putting the Bulldogs up 14-0 over UMass.

videos.headline: Simmons jets for 49-yard score
videos.description: Tyler Simmons swoops around on the reverse and bursts to the house for a 49-yard Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: UMass cuts deficit in half with 5-yard TD
videos.description: UMass RB Marquis Young finds a gap in the Georgia defense and chugs into the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown, narrowing the Bulldogs' lead to 14-7.

videos.headline: Fields darts 11-yard TD to Ridley
videos.description: Georgia backup QB Justin Fields is clocked as he throws but still whips an 11-yard touchdown to Riley Ridley.

videos.headline: Fromm fires to Simmons for long TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm flings a perfect sideline ball to Tyler Simmons, who wins the footrace to the end zone for a 72-yard Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: Fields unleashes nasty spin move
videos.description: Justin Fields keeps on the triple-option read and fools a UMass defender with a smooth spin move as he glides into the end zone.

videos.headline: Fields unloads long TD to Hardman
videos.description: Justin Fields stays patient in the pocket and heaves a 57-yard touchdown pass to Mecole Hardman to balloon Georgia's lead to 32 over UMass.
